{"title":"字符配对","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1485","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>在一个字符串中，把<strong>相同</strong>的字符<strong>两两</strong>删除，求剩下字符的个数。</p>\n<p>例如：字符串<strong style=\"\">asasda，</strong></p>\n<p>首先删除两个'<strong>a</strong>'，得到字符串'<strong>ssda</strong>'。</p>\n<p>然后删除两个'<strong>s</strong>'，得到字符串'<strong>da</strong>'。</p>\n<p>此时，字符串中没有了相同的字符，删除结束，剩下个数为2。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一个字符串，含义如描述所示。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>字符串中剩余字符的个数。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>asasda</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>字符串的长度&lt;=1,000,000（用<strong>ansistring</strong>）。</p>\n<p>字符串中只会包含小写字母。</p>\n<p>只要求输出剩余的个数。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}